Class BiMapEnumerator<T>

java.lang.Object
  uk.ac.susx.mlcl.byblo.enumerators.BiMapEnumerator<T>
Type Parameters:

All Implemented Interfaces:

Direct Known Subclasses:
JDBMStringEnumerator, MemoryBasedStringEnumerator
public class BiMapEnumerator<T>
extends Object
implements Serializable, Enumerator<T>

A simple enumerator that delegates to BiMap for enumeration storage, and assigns current max + 1 as the next key.

Author:
Hamish I A Morgan <hamish.morgan@sussex.ac.uk>
